_:Nb8c167c05bad469bb170af321d37c449 <http://schema.org/description> "The Northern Ireland Policing Board is the police authority for Northern Ireland, charged with supervising the activities of the Police Service of Northern Ireland (PSNI). NIPB is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department of Justice (Northern Ireland) ." .
